name: VR Schoool - Dinosaurs
summary:
🎓 Experience the age of dinosaurs like never before with VR Schoool: Dinosaurs. 
Walk among realistic creatures, discover their habitats and evolution, and feel the thrill of prehistoric nature in immersive Virtual Reality. 

🌐 Languages: English and Spanish.

🦖 Learn, explore, and have fun — perfect for families, students, and history lovers!
